{
  "texts": [
    "They do not care about their continued existence.",
    "Any goal that such an LLM might pursue has been determined externally.",
    "For instance, this goal is to accurately predict the next word given n previous words for generative LLMs, or to correctly translate a word from the source language to the target language for the original transformer.",
    "Pursuing that goal is also not definitive of their existence; indeed for generative LLMs, next-word-prediction is the core training objective, but the use to which they are put -and do not put themselves -can vary drastically.",
    "On the other hand, the models have cognitive autonomy."
  ]
}